Write a function called oppositeArray that takes an array arr as an argument and returns an array in which each element has been replaced with the opposite element.

Example:

the oppositeArray ([1, -2, 3]) function should return [-1, 2, -3].

Solution:

function oppositeArray(arr){
let newArr = [];
  for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++){
    newArr.push(arr[i] * -1);
  }
  return newArr;
}
